.TH "ipu_update_channel_buffer" 9 "ipu_update_channel_buffer" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ipu_update_channel_buffer \- update physical address of a channel buffer.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ipu_update_channel_buffer
.BI "(struct idmac_channel *ichan "  ","
.BI "int buffer_n "  ","
.BI "dma_addr_t phyaddr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ichan" 12
IDMAC channel.
.IP "buffer_n" 12
buffer number to update.
0 or 1 are the only valid values.
.IP "phyaddr" 12
buffer physical address.
